		<td><b>Re: What are your opinions on RF audio on the NES?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I much prefer the brighter RCA sound.<br /><br />It is very clear, though, that the 8-channel N163 Famicom games (e.g. Erika to Satoru no Yumebouken, King of Kings) were intended to be played through RF, as with 8-channels there is a very loud high frequency ringing noise that is quite unpleasant without a strong lowpass to hide it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


