		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That's what I meant. I sometimes hear it (to a lesser extent) in other games, though - I mentioned earth bound, but I've also noticed it in dragon warrior/dragon quest, and games like 'blades of steel' that use PCM. I really need to take a minute to figure out making a low pass filter sometime... Won't help with the ringing CRT sound, though.<br /><br />...also, that rick roll PCM demo, now that I think about it.<br /><br /><br />While you're here, I'd like to thank you for your Dark side of the Moon 8-bit album, by the way. I use RCA audio to listen to that one <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

